    <div class="card"><h3>How we work</h3><p class="muted">Hybrid, collaborative, constantly improving.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h3>Giving back</h3><p class="muted">B Corp certified, carbon neutral, community-minded.</p></div>
  </div>
  <div class="band" style="text-align:center;margin-top:30px"><h2>Fancy joining us?</h2><a class="btn light primary" href="/careers">See our jobs</a></div>
